#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"display-4-fs\"><strong><font class=\"text-800\"><span "
"class=\"h1-fs\">Use Case</span></font></strong></span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"display-4-fs\"><strong><font class=\"text-800\"><span "
"class=\"h1-fs\">ユースケース</span></font></strong></span>"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Basics</strong></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>基本</strong></span>"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Do you want to go further?</strong></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>更に進みますか?</strong></span>"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;"
"\">Manage your schedule and your availability in the </span></font><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Calendar App</font><font class=\"text-black\"><span "
"style=\"font-weight: normal;\">.</span></font></strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">スケ"
"ジュールと空き状況は、</span></font><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">カレンダー"
"アプリ</font><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">"
"で管理できます。</span></font></strong>"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">Odoo for Physical Therapy</span></"
"strong>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">Odoo理学療法</span></strong>"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add an upfront payment in your Appointment Type."
msgstr "アポイントメントタイプに前払の支払いを追加します。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add the Subscription App and invoice automatically based on a subscription "
"type."
msgstr ""
"サブスクリプションアプリを追加し、サブスクリプションの種類に基づいて請求書を"
"自動的に発行します。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"All emails sent and received are automatically recorded in the "
"<strong>Chatter</strong>, giving you a clear history of your communication "
"with the patient. Once the patient books an appointment, it is automatically "
"synchronized across CRM, Appointments, and Calendar, keeping your schedule "
"up to date without manual work."
msgstr ""
"送受信されたすべてのメールは、<strong>チャター</strong> に自動的に記録される"
"ため、患者との連絡の履歴を明確に把握できます。患者が予約を確定すると、その情"
"報はCRM、アポイントメント、カレンダー間で自動的に同期されるため、手作業なしで"
"スケジュールを最新の状態に保つことができます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As you review her needs, you move the opportunity to Qualified, indicating "
"that a consultation is required."
msgstr ""
"彼女のニーズを確認したら、相談が必要であることを示すために、案件を「見込みあ"
"り」のステージに進めます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Auto-post your invoice on a regular basis."
msgstr "顧客請求書を定期的に自動記帳します。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Automated recurring invoicing with the <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Subscription App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">サブスクリプションアプリ</font></"
"strong>で定期的な請求を自動化。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Be careful, using the \"Log Note\" in your contact will be displayed only "
"for you and your eventual team. If you select the \"Send message\" option, "
"this will notify your customer (which can be really interesting also)."
msgstr ""
"注意：自分の「連絡先」で 「ログメモ」を使うと、その内容は自分(および必要に応"
"じて自分のチーム)にのみ表示されます。「メッセージを送信」を選択した場合は、顧"
"客に通知されます(場合により便利です)。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Block time slots for treatments or personal availability"
msgstr "施術・私用の時間枠をブロック"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model:mail.template,name:physical_therapy.booking_suggestion
msgid "Book your next appointment"
msgstr "次回予約"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By doing this, the corresponding time slots are automatically reserved and "
"will no longer be available on the public booking link, ensuring your "
"availability remains accurate."
msgstr ""
"これにより、該当する時間枠は自動的に予約済みとなり、公開予約リンクでは選択で"
"きなくなります。その結果、空き状況が常に正確に保たれます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By installing this package, you gain access to a set of essential "
"applications, including CRM, Appointments, Calendar, and Invoicing, allowing "
"you to focus on patient care while Odoo handles your daily operations."
msgstr ""
"このパッケージをインストールすると、CRM、予約、カレンダー、請求書などの基本ア"
"プリ一式を利用できるようになります。日々の業務はOdooに任せ、患者対応に集中で"
"きます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few contacts."
msgstr ""
"このモジュールのデモデータを読み込むと、データベースにいくつかの連絡先が登録"
"されます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Cancel a session"
msgstr "セッションをキャンセル"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a dedicated <strong>knowledge article</strong> for each patient to "
"track progress, exercises, or treatment plans"
msgstr ""
"患者ごとに専用の <strong>ナレッジ記事</strong> を作成し、経過・運動課題・治療"
"計画などを記録・追跡します"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a professional <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><strong>Website</"
"strong></font> for your practice and allow patients to book appointments "
"online."
msgstr ""
"診療所向けのプロフェッショナルな<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><strong>ウェブ"
"サイト</strong></font> を作成し、患者がオンラインで予約できるようにします。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "Odoo についてさらに知るには、こちらをご覧ください："

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"During or after a therapy session, you can easily record clinical notes:"
msgstr "セラピーセッション中または終了後、臨床メモを簡単に記録できます:"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Ease your invoicing process with the <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Invoice App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">請求書</font></strong>アプリで、請求書"
"発行の手間を削減。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model:calendar.alarm,name:physical_therapy.alarm_mail_1
msgid "Follow up"
msgstr "フォローアップ"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For treatment plans that require multiple sessions (for example, 10 sessions "
"prescribed by a doctor), go to the <strong>Calendar App</strong>, create an "
"appointment, assign the patient, and set it as recurring."
msgstr ""
"複数回のセッションが必要な治療計画(例：医師が10回のセッションを処方した場合)"
"では、<strong>カレンダーアプリ</strong>に移動して予約を作成し、患者を割り当"
"て、繰り返し予定に設定してください。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From Emily's opportunity in the CRM, you can invite her to book her first "
"session in just a few clicks."
msgstr ""
"CRMのEmilyの案件から、数回クリックするだけで初回セッションの予約に招待できま"
"す。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "From there, you can:"
msgstr "そこから、以下の操作が可能です："

#. module: physical_therapy
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/physical_therapy/static/src/js/my_tour.js:0
msgid "Get on track and explore our recommendations for your Odoo usage here!"
msgstr "Odoo活用のヒントやおすすめ設定を、ここからチェックしてみましょう!"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr ""

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you navigate to the Invoice App, you can manage your invoices. You have "
"many possibilities to streamline your invoicing process:"
msgstr ""
"請求書アプリに移動すると、顧客請求書の管理ができます。請求プロセスを合理化す"
"る方法は沢山あります。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you only need to invoice part of a session or treatment plan to the "
"patient (for example, X% paid by the patient while the rest is covered by "
"insurance or a mutual fund), you can use a down payment."
msgstr ""
"患者に対してセッション/治療プランの一部だけを請求したい場合(例：患者がX%を負"
"担し、残りは保険や共済が負担する場合)は、前受金(頭金)を利用できます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In the <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><strong>CRM App</strong></font>, you "
"create a new opportunity for Emily, recording her contact details and the "
"reason for consultation (e.g. back pain, postural issues, rehabilitation)."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><strong>CRM</strong></font>アプリでは、エミ"
"リーの新しい案件を作成し、連絡先情報と相談理由(例：腰痛、姿勢の問題、リハビリ"
"テーション)を記録します。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model:crm.stage,name:physical_therapy.crm_stage_5
msgid "Inactive"
msgstr "非アクティブ"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoice yourself, manually."
msgstr "手動で顧客請求書を作成して下さい。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Let's Try"
msgstr "試してみましょう"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model:mail.template,subject:physical_therapy.booking_suggestion
msgid "Looking forward to meeting you"
msgstr "お目にかかれるのを楽しみにしております"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo<strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Marketing Automation </font></strong>,"
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Email Marketing</font></strong>,"
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Social Media Marketing </font></"
"strong>, and <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS Marketing </font></"
"strong>."
msgstr ""
"Odoo<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> マーケティングオートメーション </"
"font></strong>、<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">メールマーケティング</"
"font></strong>、<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> ソーシャルメディア"
"マーケティング </font></strong>、<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS"
"マーケティング </font></strong>で、あらゆるコミュニケーションチャネルを一か所"
"で管理できます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting App</font></"
"strong>)"
msgstr ""
"これまで以上に簡単に会計を管理できる、完全統合型の環境をご活用ください。"
"(<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">会計アプリ</font></strong>)"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your team's and integrate them in all processes by adding "
"the<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Employees App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">従業員アプリ</font></strong>を追加して"
"チームを管理し、全てのプロセスに統合しましょう。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Move or reschedule the appointment (the patient is notified automatically)"
msgstr "予約を移動または変更する(患者には自動的に通知されます)"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to manage your entire "
"business from your phone."
msgstr ""
"Odooはアプリで一元化されています。ダウンロードすれば、スマートフォンからビジ"
"ネス全体を管理できます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odooは無限の可能性を提供します:"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"これはパッケージに含まれる機能の概要にすぎません。新しいアプリを追加したり、"
"デモデータを削除/変更したり、自由にテストしてみましょう!"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once an appointment is booked, you can see it in the <strong>Calendar App</"
"strong>."
msgstr "予約が完了すると、<strong>カレンダーアプリ</strong> で確認できます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model:crm.stage,name:physical_therapy.crm_stage_6
msgid "Redirect to Another Practitioner"
msgstr "別の担当医に転院"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model:product.template,name:physical_therapy.product_product_3_product_template
msgid "Running analysis and injury prevention"
msgstr "ランニング分析・けが予防"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Schedule a demo"
msgstr "デモを予約する"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model:mail.template,description:physical_therapy.booking_suggestion
msgid "Sent to all attendees if a reminder is set"
msgstr "リマインダが設定されている場合、参加者全員に送信"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Appointments App</font><font "
"class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> manages your "
"appointment types and allows patients to book consultation.</span></"
"font><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"/></strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">予約</font><font class=\"text-"
"black\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">アプリでは予約タイプを管理でき、"
"患者が相談予約を行えます。</span></font><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"/></"
"strong>"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM App</font></strong>(Customer "
"Relationship Management) helps you manage patient inquiries and follow-ups."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRMアプリ</font></strong> (顧客関係管"
"理)は、患者からの問い合わせやフォローアップの管理を支援します。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Appointments App</strong> and <strong>Calendar App</strong> are "
"fully synchronized, ensuring your availability is always up to date."
msgstr ""
"<strong>予約</strong>アプリと<strong>カレンダー</strong>アプリは完全に同期し"
"ており、空き状況は常に最新に保たれます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Odoo Calendar App is compatible with Outlook and Google Calendar. "
"Activate the sync in the Calendar App settings."
msgstr ""
"Odooカレンダーアプリは、OutlookおよびGoogleカレンダーと互換性があります。カレ"
"ンダーアプリの設定で同期を有効化して下さい。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The down payment is deducted from the final invoice, keeping billing clear "
"and accurate for both the patient and the insurer."
msgstr ""
"前受金は最終請求書から差し引かれるため、患者様・保険者（保険会社）の双方に"
"とって、請求内容を明確かつ正確に保てます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model:appointment.type,name:physical_therapy.appointment_type_1
#: model:product.template,name:physical_therapy.product_product_2_product_template
msgid "Therapy Session"
msgstr "セラピー・セッション"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"これらはすべて、現在ご契約中のサブスクリプションで無料でご利用いただけます!🙃"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This industry package is designed specifically for physical therapy and "
"rehabilitation practices, including kinesiotherapists, physiotherapists, "
"osteopaths, and other rehabilitation and therapy professionals, helping you "
"manage your patients, appointments, and billing in one fully integrated "
"system."
msgstr ""
"このインダストリー向けパッケージは、キネシオセラピスト、理学療法士、オステオ"
"パシー療法士、その他のリハビリテーションおよび療法の専門家を含む、理学療法お"
"よびリハビリテーションの診療現場向けに特別に設計されており、患者、予約、請求"
"管理を1つの完全に統合されたシステムで一元管理できるよう支援します。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This is especially useful when sessions are prescribed by a doctor and need "
"to be tracked accurately."
msgstr ""
"これは、医師によってセッションが処方され、正確に追跡する必要がある場合に特に"
"有用です。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To begin, you'll find the key applications you need on your Odoo dashboard. "
"Let's take a closer look at how you can use these tools."
msgstr ""

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To configure this, click the <strong>gear icon</strong> at the top of a CRM "
"column and select <strong>Automation</strong>, or add automated emails "
"directly in the <strong>Appointment Type</strong> settings."
msgstr ""
"これを設定するには、CRMの各列の上部にある<strong>歯車アイコン</strong>をク"
"リックし、<strong>自動化</strong>を選択します。あるいは、<strong>予約タイプ</"
"strong>の設定画面で自動メールを直接追加できます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "To do so, go to CRM &gt; Configuration &gt; Sales Teams."
msgstr "そのためには、CRM &gt; 設定 &gt; 販売チームに移動します。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To follow up on a patient's treatment plan, you can quickly see how many "
"sessions have already been completed by clicking the <strong>Appointments "
"stat button</strong> on the patient’s contact form."
msgstr ""
"患者の治療計画をフォローするには、患者の連絡先フォームにある<strong>予約</"
"strong>の統計ボタンをクリックすると、完了済みのセッション数をすぐに確認できま"
"す。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To reduce your no show rate drastically, appointments automatically come "
"with reminders by Email and SMS."
msgstr ""
"ノーショー(無断キャンセル)を大幅に減らすため、予約にはメール/SMSのリマインダ"
"が自動で設定されています。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use <strong>Log Note</strong> on the patient's contact to keep internal "
"treatment notes"
msgstr ""
"患者の連絡先にある<strong>ログメモ</strong>を使用して、社内用の治療メモを残せ"
"ます"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Using the Chatter on the right side of the opportunity, click <strong>Send a "
"message</strong>, select the “<strong>Book your next appointment</strong>” "
"email template, and send it to the patient. The email contains a direct "
"booking link, allowing the patient to select an available time slot and book "
"the appointment online."
msgstr ""
"案件の右側にあるチャターで<strong>メッセージを送信</strong>をクリックし、メー"
"ルテンプレート「<strong>次回予約</strong>」を選択して患者に送信します。メール"
"には直接予約できるリンクが含まれており、患者は空き時間枠を選んでオンラインで"
"予約できます。"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Welcome to the Odoo Physical Therapy package!"
msgstr "Odoo 理学療法パッケージへようこそ！"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:physical_therapy.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "ようこそ！"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When an appointment is completed, automatically send a follow-up email "
"suggesting the next session"
msgstr ""
"予定が完了したら、次のセッションを提案するフォローアップメールを自動的に送信"

#. module: physical_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:physical_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When an opportunity moves to <strong>“Qualified”</strong>, automatically "
"send the booking email to the patient"
msgstr ""
"案件が<strong>「見込みあり」</strong> に移行した際、患者に予約確認メールを自"
"動的に送信"

